cs.DB, cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.CY 

This paper discusses the security and privacy concerns related to outsourcing databases to the cloud, which falls under the scope of database systems (cs.DB) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). It also discusses the challenges related to scalability and availability, which are topics in distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions the need for secure software engineering practices (cs.SE) and compliance with legal regulations (cs.CY) to ensure data privacy in cloud databases.
